(8301, 'ferumoxides', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Administration provides elemental iron. In patients who are receiving supplemental iron orally or parenterally, the dose of supplemental iron may need to be decreased.The effect of concomitant parenteral iron on Feridex I.V.', 'DailyMed'),
