(8301, 'elvitegravir, cobicistat, emtricitabine, and tenofovir disoproxil fumarate', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Sedative/hypnotics: Benzodiazepines:e.g.Parenterally administered midazolamclorazepatediazepamestazolamflurazepambuspironezolpidem ↑ sedatives/hypnotics Concomitant use of parenteral midazolam with STRIBILD may increase plasma concentrations of midazolam.', 'DailyMed'),
