(29484, 'quinapril', 'N/A', 'moderate', 'If concomitant therapy of quinaprilhydrochloride with potassium-sparing diuretics (eg, spironolactone, triamterene, or amiloride),potassium supplements, or potassium-containing salt substitutes is indicated, they should be usedwith caution along with appropriate monitoring of serum potassium (see PRECAUTIONS).', 'DailyMed'),
