(1664, 'anagrelide hydrochloride', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Drug interaction studies have not been conducted with the other common medications used concomitantly with anagrelide in clinical trials which were acetaminophen, furosemide, iron, ranitidine, hydroxyurea, and allopurinol.', 'DailyMed'),
