(4560, 'darunavir ethanolate and cobicistat', 'N/A', 'moderate', 'Buspirone, diazepam, estazolam, zolpidem ↑ sedatives/hypnotics With concomitant use, titration is recommended with sedatives/hypnotics metabolized by CYP3A and a lower dose of the sedatives/hypnotics should be considered with monitoring for increased and prolonged effects or adverse reactions.', 'DailyMed'),
