(4650, 'omeprazole dr', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Like with other drugs that decrease the intragastric acidity, the absorption of drugs such as ketoconazole, ampicillin esters, iron salts and erlotinib can decrease, while the absorption of drugs such as digoxin can increase during treatment with omeprazole.', 'DailyMed'),
