(4650, 'ferric maltol', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Concomitant use of some drugs may reduce the bioavailability of iron after administration of ACCRUFER. 7.2 Effect of ACCRUFER on Other Drugs Dimercaprol Concomitant use of iron products with dimercaprol may increase the risk of nephrotoxicity.', 'DailyMed'),
