(30238, 'lisinopril', 'N/A', 'major', 'Use of lisinopril with potassium-sparing diuretics (e.g., spironolactone,eplerenone,triamterene or amiloride), potassium supplements, or potassium-containing salt substitutes may lead to significant increases in serum potassium.', 'DailyMed'),
